title: Exclusive: Watch Sleepy Hollow's New Opening Credits
text: Posted Oct. 22, 2015 at 6:09 PM Updated at 8:59 PM Posted Oct. 22, 2015 at 6:09 PM Updated at 8:59 PM There will be a few new faces in Sleepy Hollow 's opening credits on Thursday. Sleepy's new opening credits will officially welcome new stars Zach Appelman and Lance Gross , who play Joe Corbin and Daniel Reynolds, respectively. In the episode itself, Pandora will unleash her most evil creature yet, the Tooth Fairy. In order to protect the children of Sleepy Hollow from this new threat, Abbie and Jenny join together to kick butt in a way only the Mills sisters can. Check out Sleepy Hollow 's new opening credits above. Sleepy Hollow airs Thursdays at 9/8c on Fox. Other Links From TVGuide.com
